sentence: how many first class flights does united airlines have departing from boston today
sq2:
SELECT  COUNT(*), '"'||v0.airline_code||'"' FROM flight v0 
WHERE ((v0.airline_code = 'UA') AND ((v0.flight_days IN (
SELECT v1.days_code FROM days v1 
WHERE (v1.day_name IN (
SELECT v2.day_name FROM date_day v2 
WHERE (((v2.year =  1993) AND (v2.month_number =  4)) 
AND (v2.day_number =  29)))))) AND ((v0.from_airport IN (
SELECT v3.airport_code FROM airport_service v3 
WHERE (v3.city_code IN (
SELECT v4.city_code FROM city v4 
WHERE (v4.city_name = 'BOSTON'))))) AND (v0.flight_id IN (
SELECT v5.flight_id FROM flight_fare v5 
WHERE (v5.fare_id IN (
SELECT v6.fare_id FROM fare v6 
WHERE ((v6.fare_basis_code IN (
SELECT v7.fare_basis_code FROM fare_basis v7 
WHERE (v7.class_type = 'FIRST'))) 
AND (v6.fare_basis_code IN (
SELECT v8.fare_basis_code FROM fare_basis v8 
WHERE (v8.basis_days IN (
SELECT v9.days_code FROM days v9 
WHERE (v9.day_name IN (
SELECT v10.day_name FROM date_day v10 
WHERE (((v10.year =  1993) 
AND (v10.month_number =  4)) AND (v10.day_number =  29)))))))))))))))) GROUP BY v0.airline_code;
